entially flat and the market is RANGE_BOUND; a modest 5-day rise does not override the larger set of supply/inventory indicators, especially with price still well below the 200-day SMA. Finally, the Volatility Analyst highlights elevated IV and bearish skew (put/call premium ratio > 1), which is consistent with downside hedging demand; per the framework, expensive/defensive options sentiment warrants caution and prevents upgrading conviction to the highest tier even though the fundamental evidence tilts bearish. [Consensus ALIGNED (Vote=BEARISH)] [VOL WARNING: Options expensive. Spread costs elevated. Thesis: PLAUSIBLE]', 'regime': 'HIGH_VOLATILITY', 'volatility_sentiment': 'BEARISH', 'confidence': 0.8, 'price': 292.9, 'sma_200': 326.59375, 'expected_price': 292.9, 'predicted_return': 0.0, 'thesis_strength': 'PLAUSIBLE', 'conviction_multiplier': 1.0, '_cycle_id': 'KC-4be00f0a'}, {'contract_month': '202607', 'prediction_type': 'DIRECTIONAL', 'direction': 'NEUTRAL', 'reason': 'NO TRADE: Direction neutral, no positive-EV vol trade. (vol=BULLISH, regime=HIGH_VOLATILITY, conflict=0.56)', 'regime': 'HIGH_VOLATILITY', 'volatility_sentiment': 'BULLISH', 'confidence': 0.6, 'price': 286.5, 'sma_200': 317.31925, 'expected_price': 286.5, 'predicted_return': 0.0, 'thesis_strength': 'PLAUSIBLE', 'conviction_multiplier': 0.75, '_cycle_id': 'KC-80a2b3c7'}, {'contract_month': '202609', 'prediction_type': 'DIRECTIONAL', 'direction': 'NEUTRAL', 'reason': 'NO TRADE: Direction neutral, no positive-EV vol trade. (vol=BULLISH, regime=HIGH_VOLATILITY, conflict=0.24)', 'regime': 'HIGH_VOLATILITY', 'volatility_sentiment': 'BULLISH', 'confidence': 0.6, 'price': 278.0, 'sma_200': 308.0725, 'expected_price': 278.0, 'predicted_return': 0.0, 'thesis_strength': 'PLAUSIBLE', 'conviction_multiplier': 0.75, '_cycle_id': 'KC-b89248c2'}, {'contract_month': '202612', 'prediction_type': 'DIRECTIONAL', 'direction': 'NEUTRAL', 'reason': 'NO TRADE: Direction neutral, no positive-EV vol trade. (vol=NEUTRAL, 